# Vistas Razor (Practica 2)

## Layouts

- CRUD interno / consultas: `~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml`
- Login/registro externo (si aplica): `~/Views/Shared/_LayoutExterno.cshtml`

Personalizar `_Layout` con mensaje de bienvenida y 3 opciones de menú (enunciado).

## Formulario

```cshtml
@model Practica2.Web.Models.ClienteModel
@{ Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml"; }

@using (Html.BeginForm("Registrar", "Clientes", FormMethod.Post, new { @id = "RegistrarClienteForm" }))
{
    if (ViewBag.Mensaje != null)
    {
        <div class="alert text-danger" role="alert">@ViewBag.Mensaje</div>
    }
    <div class="form-group position-relative has-icon-left">
        @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.Cedula, new { @class = "form-control form-control-xl", @placeholder = "Cédula" })
        <div class="form-control-icon"><i class="bi bi-person-badge"></i></div>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg shadow-lg mt-3">Procesar</button>
}

@section scripts {
    <script src="~/Scripts/registrar-cliente.js"></script>
}
```

## Convenciones

- `Html.BeginForm` + `Html.TextBoxFor` / `Html.DropDownListFor`
- Navegación: `@Url.Action("Action", "Controller")`
- Internas: `.page-title` > `.section` > `.card`
- Botón submit: **Procesar**
- FK Mascotas: dropdown de clientes con `DropDownListFor(m => m.IdCliente, ...)`
